Protocols/MapEncodable.html.name: MapEncodable
Protocols/MapEncodable.html.abstract: A protocol that adds support of complex objects to be serialized into a json object.

Protocols/MapDecodable.html.name: MapDecodable
Protocols/MapDecodable.html.abstract: A protocol that adds support of complex objects to be deserialized from a json object.

Protocols.html#/s:13MapCodableKit0aB0P.name: MapCodable
Protocols.html#/s:13MapCodableKit0aB0P.abstract: A wrapper protocol that reqires both MapEncodable and MapDecodable protocols.

Protocols/MapDecoder.html.name: MapDecoder
Protocols/MapDecoder.html.abstract: A protocol that allows you to transform a MapPrimitive (JSON) value to another value. This protocol is used to add more type sypport to the Map class.

Protocols/MapEncoder.html.name: MapEncoder
Protocols/MapEncoder.html.abstract: A protocol that allows you to transform a value into a MapPrimitive (JSON) value. This protocol is used to add more type support to the Map class.

Protocols/MapKey.html.name: MapKey
Protocols/MapKey.html.abstract: A MapKey is a protocol that provides a parsing mechanism for converting any object (such as a String) into key parts (an array of KeyPart objects). Key parts individually represent a key in a json dictionary or position in an array. When combined, key parts represent the nesting structure of a JSON dictionary for a specific value, object or array. The order of key parts matter as they coencide with the nesting order in a dictionary.

Protocols.html#/s:13MapCodableKit0A9Prim.name: MapPrimitive
Protocols.html#/s:13MapCodableKit0A9Prim.abstract: A protocol that represents json primatives as well as arrays and dictionaries of map primatives.

Enums/MapDecodingError.html.name: MapDecodingError
Enums/MapDecodingError.html.abstract: An error that is returned when attempting to return an object from a Map.

Enums/MapEncodingError.html.name: MapEncodingError
Enums/MapEncodingError.html.abstract: An error that is returned when attempting to add an object to a Map.

Enums/KeyPart.html.name: KeyPart
Enums/KeyPart.html.abstract: A key that represents a value or object in a dictionary. A KeyPart also conforms to a MapKey.
